WEBVTT

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.940
笙ｪOnly after bloom comes fruit笙ｪ

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:28.320
笙ｪWho says glory must fade to the past笙ｪ

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.070
笙ｪOnly through thunder
do you reach the clouds笙ｪ

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:42.180
笙ｪWho made you the crown of every peak笙ｪ

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.990
笙ｪI stand at the center of the stage笙ｪ

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.060
笙ｪMy shadow is pinned against the wall笙ｪ

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.720
笙ｪFacing the light earns every medal笙ｪ

00:00:56.760 --> 00:00:59.940
笙ｪLittle birds,
save your needless pecking笙ｪ

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:03.220
笙ｪThe open sky rises high笙ｪ

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.890
笙ｪWhen night falls,
the moon begins to shine笙ｪ

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.920
笙ｪI stand in the heart of these lands笙ｪ

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.280
笙ｪMy shadow bears no crown or robe笙ｪ

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:22.360
笙ｪThen I know truth needs no disguise笙ｪ

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:26.020
笙ｪThe green hills see me as I am笙ｪ

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.350
笙ｪLike dew, lightning,
and moon on the river笙ｪ

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:33.790
笙ｪShowing me exactly who I am笙ｪ

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:35.040
=The Lead=

00:01:36.112 --> 00:01:37.856
=Episode 45=

00:02:40.959 --> 00:02:42.439
Troupe Leader.

00:03:03.104 --> 00:03:04.768
(Grave of Liu Hongbing)

00:03:04.768 --> 00:03:07.040
(Grave of Beloved Son, Liu Yi)

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.824
(Grave of Loving Father, Shan Yangping)

00:03:09.824 --> 00:03:12.448
(Grave of Loving Father, Song Guangzu)

00:03:15.998 --> 00:03:20.080
(Five years later)

00:03:23.719 --> 00:03:30.400
笙ｪDon't stop me笙ｪ

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:39.400
笙ｪLet me bear the consequences alone笙ｪ

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:45.879
Put Dou E in shackles and jail her.

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:46.759
Take her away.

00:03:46.759 --> 00:03:47.280
Dou E.

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.479
Go.

00:03:48.479 --> 00:03:49.360
Mother-in-law.

00:03:49.719 --> 00:03:50.319
Dou E.

00:03:50.319 --> 00:03:51.120
Mother-in-law.

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:51.759
Dou E.

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:52.352
Go.

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:53.000
Go.

00:03:53.159 --> 00:03:54.319
Mother-in-law.

00:03:54.319 --> 00:03:55.680
Dou E.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:56.280
Mother-in-law.

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.120
Go.

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:58.272
Dou E.

00:03:58.272 --> 00:03:58.919
Go.

00:03:58.919 --> 00:03:59.840
Mother-in-law.

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:03.759
Dou E.

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:10.840
Court dismissed!

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.680
Order!

00:04:14.360 --> 00:04:15.400
Hurry.

00:04:16.199 --> 00:04:16.919
Faster.

00:04:17.919 --> 00:04:18.680
Time's tight.

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:21.639
Faster.

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:24.919
Waist tie.

00:04:25.719 --> 00:04:26.272
Waist tie.

00:04:29.599 --> 00:04:30.360
Done.

00:04:31.439 --> 00:04:32.240
Hurry.

00:04:38.039 --> 00:04:39.319
Step aside. Hurry.

00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:40.439
Help me change.

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:41.960
Hurry.

00:04:41.960 --> 00:04:43.080
Yes, here.

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:55.319
Faster.

00:04:57.439 --> 00:04:58.439
Faster.

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:07.960
笙ｪInjustice笙ｪ

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:18.919
笙ｪWithout any cause笙ｪ

00:05:21.599 --> 00:05:32.879
笙ｪI am said to have violated the law笙ｪ

00:05:43.879 --> 00:05:46.520
笙ｪAnd so I face笙ｪ

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:47.599
Hold it.

00:05:47.599 --> 00:05:51.936
- 笙ｪCruel torture笙ｪ
- Come on.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:54.000
You got this.

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:57.199
Done.

00:05:57.759 --> 00:05:58.959
I've tied it on the back.

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:20.439
Mr. Qin.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:23.759
What is it, Troupe Leader?

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:25.079
Don't call me that.

00:06:25.279 --> 00:06:27.639
With you, I'll always be Guisheng.

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:29.720
Today is the Mid-Autumn Festival.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.639
I thought you might be alone.

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:33.319
Let me treat you to a meal.

00:06:34.279 --> 00:06:35.319
Let's catch up.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:39.120
- Want to read my new script?
- That's right.

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:43.319
Master Hu told me that it's excellent.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:46.920
He said it's the best script
you've ever written.

00:06:47.519 --> 00:06:48.519
What else did he say?

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:51.279
Mr. Qin.

00:06:51.839 --> 00:06:52.800
We have

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.920
several opera award winners
in the troupe.

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.319
They're great performers.

00:06:57.839 --> 00:06:59.759
Don't let your script go to waste.

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:02.439
Mr. Qin.

00:07:03.519 --> 00:07:04.680
Master Hu told me

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:06.120
that if Qin'e doesn't perform,

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:08.560
you'll burn this script

00:07:08.839 --> 00:07:11.000
and take it to your grave.

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:12.079
Is that true?

00:07:12.439 --> 00:07:14.839
If Master Hu said so, then yes.

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:17.360
My dearest Mr. Qin, you can't do that...

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:18.176
Shh.

00:07:19.639 --> 00:07:21.199
Talk to Master Hu about it.

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:22.199
But...

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:33.560
Mr. Qin.

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:36.759
Did you read my script?

00:07:38.680 --> 00:07:39.720
I can't sing it.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:43.519
I wrote this script for you.

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:47.079
My wife said only you could sing it
before she passed away.

00:07:47.600 --> 00:07:48.560
Mr. Qin.

00:07:48.959 --> 00:07:50.639
I really can't sing it.

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:54.480
We have many young talents
in the troupe now.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:57.720
Give it to them and let them perform it.

00:08:05.855 --> 00:08:10.720
笙ｪMy cry shakes heaven and earth笙ｪ

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:12.240
Don't make the stitches too tight.

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:15.839
Leave the performers and the play
some breathing room.

00:08:34.244 --> 00:08:45.664
笙ｪBut gods and ghosts笙ｪ

00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:58.304
笙ｪProve deaf and blind笙ｪ

00:09:02.327 --> 00:09:11.520
笙ｪSun and moon笙ｪ

00:09:19.833 --> 00:09:32.128
笙ｪIf you cannot tell right from wrong,
why do you bother to rise笙ｪ

00:09:34.439 --> 00:09:35.360
Xiaohui.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:42.496
Auntie.

00:09:45.800 --> 00:09:46.399
I'll do it.

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:47.008
Here.

00:09:51.543 --> 00:09:56.896
笙ｪThe wicked who deserve to die笙ｪ

00:09:59.160 --> 00:10:00.800
One million is really not enough.

00:10:01.800 --> 00:10:02.879
Too little.

00:10:03.439 --> 00:10:04.480
At least

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:06.480
three million.

00:10:06.959 --> 00:10:08.919
Sir, four rounds.

00:10:08.919 --> 00:10:09.639
Here's the money.

00:10:09.639 --> 00:10:11.360
- Leave it there.
- One million may work.

00:10:12.512 --> 00:10:13.240
Okay.

00:10:14.600 --> 00:10:15.679
Okay, fine.

00:10:15.679 --> 00:10:16.360
That's it.

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:21.000
You have some steel materials, right?

00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:24.480
Wang Sanwa from Diaojia Village

00:10:24.879 --> 00:10:26.960
needs twenty tons of steel
for something urgent.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.080
Want to talk to him?

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:29.000
I have his number.

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:30.080
How did you know?

00:10:30.360 --> 00:10:32.320
He made a call here,
and I wrote it down.

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:36.679
That guy's a fraud, full of nonsense.
Never trust him.

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:38.080
Really?

00:10:38.799 --> 00:10:39.879
Pay the phone bill.

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:41.080
How much is it?

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:42.080
Two yuan.

00:10:43.039 --> 00:10:46.200
It was a local call, not long-distance.
Two yuan? Make it one.

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:48.879
Come on.

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:51.759
You talk about
business deals worth millions.

00:10:51.759 --> 00:10:53.759
But you haggle over a phone bill.

00:10:53.759 --> 00:10:57.120
Save where you can
and spend where you must.

00:10:58.039 --> 00:11:00.000
What a great actor.

00:11:01.600 --> 00:11:03.000
You can be a tycoon.

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:09.679
Got rejected again?

00:11:10.399 --> 00:11:12.440
With the exact same lines.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:14.679
You shouldn't have bothered.

00:11:15.919 --> 00:11:18.240
I'm telling you, she's done for.

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:20.960
Can't reason with her.

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:22.480
She could drive you mad.

00:11:22.879 --> 00:11:26.879
I would've brought her sister out
if she hadn't been so pitiful.

00:11:27.679 --> 00:11:29.039
I should've brought her sister

00:11:29.039 --> 00:11:31.264
and left her in the mountains
to herd sheep

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.480
for the rest of her life.

00:11:35.759 --> 00:11:38.799
She was crying
and begging me to bring her out.

00:11:40.120 --> 00:11:40.960
So I chose her.

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:43.519
I've dedicated my whole life to her.

00:11:44.639 --> 00:11:46.480
I even came to Chang'an because of her.

00:11:47.120 --> 00:11:48.279
There are good reasons

00:11:49.279 --> 00:11:50.799
to come to Chang'an.

00:11:51.399 --> 00:11:52.320
Like what?

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.320
Hello, Mr. Qin.

00:11:59.159 --> 00:12:01.080
Hei is out. Did you see him?

00:12:01.080 --> 00:12:01.639
Who?

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:02.840
Hei.

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:06.000
He came by at noon but didn't see you.

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:07.360
He was just released yesterday.

00:12:07.799 --> 00:12:09.879
But it's only been a little over a year.

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:12.399
We haven't had peace for long.

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:14.039
Let's go.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:16.639
Weihua Barbecue. Let's grab a drink.

00:12:17.919 --> 00:12:20.200
Mr. Qin is upset.
I'll have a drink with him.

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:21.240
Keep an eye on the stall.

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:23.159
Don't drink too much.

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:27.159
I've never seen anyone like her.

00:12:28.480 --> 00:12:30.320
When people suffer a blow,

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:32.519
they hurt for a while and mope.

00:12:32.879 --> 00:12:33.879
They take a break.

00:12:33.879 --> 00:12:36.519
But it's been years,
and she still hasn't gotten over it.

00:12:37.039 --> 00:12:39.399
She can't get on stage and perform.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:44.000
I've never seen that.

00:13:15.159 --> 00:13:15.879
You brat.

00:13:22.559 --> 00:13:24.200
Come on, drink.

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:27.799
You haven't paid back that 30,000 yuan?

00:13:28.919 --> 00:13:29.600
Why should I?

00:13:30.399 --> 00:13:31.879
The interest keeps compounding.

00:13:32.240 --> 00:13:33.519
I owe him 100,000 now.

00:13:33.960 --> 00:13:34.600
How am I

00:13:34.600 --> 00:13:35.639
going to pay him back?

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:39.240
Loan-sharking is illegal.
You should call the police.

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:40.879
This guy

00:13:41.879 --> 00:13:44.879
got into a fight
and was locked up for a year.

00:13:46.399 --> 00:13:47.799
I'll give him a break.

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:50.519
Then I'll call the police on him.

00:13:51.799 --> 00:13:54.399
You can't just hide
every time you see him.

00:13:54.919 --> 00:13:57.320
Do you need some money to tide you over?

00:13:57.919 --> 00:13:59.679
Why are you playing the good guy now?

00:14:01.919 --> 00:14:04.919
Back when Qin'e and Hongbing
were struggling

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:06.600
to cure their kid,

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:07.759
why didn't you lend me money?

00:14:08.279 --> 00:14:09.879
You just turned your head away.

00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:12.039
When did you borrow money from me?

00:14:13.360 --> 00:14:14.360
Did you forget?

00:14:14.879 --> 00:14:16.080
Or are you playing dumb?

00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:17.679
Do you have dementia?

00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:21.320
Hard to say which of us has dementia.

00:14:22.559 --> 00:14:23.279
Just tell me.

00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:24.000
Want the money?

00:14:24.279 --> 00:14:25.960
No, money talk hurts feelings.

00:14:27.360 --> 00:14:28.240
Fine.

00:14:28.679 --> 00:14:29.360
I'll keep it

00:14:29.559 --> 00:14:31.296
for Qin'e's new play.

00:14:31.296 --> 00:14:33.240
Talking about her hurts even more.

00:14:35.360 --> 00:14:35.879
Also,

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:38.840
stop spouting nonsense to everyone

00:14:39.480 --> 00:14:42.440
about me burning my script
and taking it to my grave.

00:14:42.799 --> 00:14:44.000
So much nonsense.

00:14:44.320 --> 00:14:45.159
How's that nonsense?

00:14:46.600 --> 00:14:48.120
Back when your wife passed...

00:14:48.639 --> 00:14:49.559
Tofu Beauty...

00:14:50.559 --> 00:14:52.480
Didn't she say that only Qin'e

00:14:53.039 --> 00:14:54.039
could do your new play?

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:56.720
If Qin'e doesn't perform it,

00:14:56.720 --> 00:14:59.399
you should burn the script
and take it to your grave.

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:00.720
Didn't she say that?

00:15:01.200 --> 00:15:02.440
When did she say that?

00:15:02.840 --> 00:15:03.679
She told you?

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.279
She told you.

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:06.559
I was listening there.

00:15:09.799 --> 00:15:11.559
She was silent her whole life.

00:15:12.799 --> 00:15:15.039
If only she could've said so much to me

00:15:16.679 --> 00:15:17.399
before leaving.

00:15:24.080 --> 00:15:24.840
Come on, drink.

00:15:25.279 --> 00:15:25.960
Stop zoning out.

00:15:29.879 --> 00:15:32.360
May we all live long
and share the moonlight

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:39.240
though a thousand miles apart.

00:16:21.879 --> 00:16:22.879
(Over the years,)

00:16:23.200 --> 00:16:24.840
(for some reason,)

00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:27.879
(Yi Qin'e simply couldn't
open her mouth)

00:16:28.519 --> 00:16:30.399
(to sing again.)

00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:32.720
(She kept blaming herself.)

00:16:33.480 --> 00:16:35.799
(She blamed herself
for being so clueless about life.)

00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:39.440
(She blamed herself
for choosing to perform that day,)

00:16:40.279 --> 00:16:43.559
(which ended up harming
so many innocent people.)

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:47.759
(She felt that 24 hours in a day
were far too long.)

00:16:48.320 --> 00:16:50.879
(After finishing work,)

00:16:51.240 --> 00:16:53.024
(grocery shopping, and cleaning,)

00:16:53.024 --> 00:16:55.960
(time would suddenly fall empty.)

00:16:56.600 --> 00:16:57.759
(She often had no idea)

00:16:57.919 --> 00:17:01.639
(what to do with the remaining hours.)

00:17:02.679 --> 00:17:04.159
(To avoid thinking about it,)

00:17:04.159 --> 00:17:05.960
(she worked herself to the bone,)

00:17:06.440 --> 00:17:08.200
(over and over,)

00:17:09.159 --> 00:17:10.880
(using this memory-filled home)

00:17:10.912 --> 00:17:13.320
(to wash away her sins.)

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:15.200
(She dreaded nightfall)

00:17:15.799 --> 00:17:17.039
(and those sleepless nights)

00:17:17.320 --> 00:17:20.720
(when old memories
would replay in her mind)

00:17:21.320 --> 00:17:22.320
(like a movie,)

00:17:22.960 --> 00:17:25.960
(over and over, without an ending.)

00:17:26.879 --> 00:17:28.360
(Yet she also longed for nightfall,)

00:17:29.279 --> 00:17:32.919
(because she would dream again
when she could actually sleep.)

00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:34.399
(In her dreams,)

00:17:34.919 --> 00:17:37.879
(she was no longer that freak
who could only sing opera.)

00:17:38.639 --> 00:17:39.399
(In her dreams,)

00:17:40.120 --> 00:17:42.799
(Liu Hongbing and Liu Yi would return.)

00:17:43.639 --> 00:17:44.480
(In her dreams,)

00:17:44.600 --> 00:17:47.720
(she would say all the words to him)

00:17:48.120 --> 00:17:50.080
(she had kept unsaid all these years.)

00:17:51.240 --> 00:17:52.679
(Only later did she learn)

00:17:53.039 --> 00:17:55.960
(this condition actually had a name.)

00:17:56.559 --> 00:18:00.120
(Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder.)

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:03.399
(And she was very, very ill.)

00:19:43.640 --> 00:19:45.440
Madam, give me two of these.

00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:47.039
Yeah.

00:19:50.039 --> 00:19:51.000
How much is it?

00:19:57.759 --> 00:19:59.279
Bring your household registry book

00:19:59.759 --> 00:20:01.039
and ID card.

00:20:01.640 --> 00:20:02.880
Bring all these documents.

00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:04.480
Then we can get started.

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:07.519
Does your child
have any artistic talents?

00:20:08.160 --> 00:20:08.759
No?

00:20:10.119 --> 00:20:11.160
Then we'll just...

00:20:12.119 --> 00:20:12.880
Lili.

00:20:14.119 --> 00:20:15.240
Excuse me for a second.

00:20:16.440 --> 00:20:17.119
Lili.

00:20:17.359 --> 00:20:19.640
What brought you back from Hainan?

00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:21.519
My kid's back for the Gaokao.

00:20:21.519 --> 00:20:22.039
Come on.

00:20:22.039 --> 00:20:23.279
Or I wouldn't come back.

00:20:23.279 --> 00:20:24.279
Life is great there.

00:20:25.160 --> 00:20:26.400
Your kid has grown so tall.

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:27.759
- Say hi to Uncle Liu.
- So handsome.

00:20:27.759 --> 00:20:28.920
- Hello, Uncle Liu.
- Hello.

00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:29.880
Let's head inside.

00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:30.480
Let's go.

00:20:31.519 --> 00:20:32.279
Where's Liang?

00:20:32.640 --> 00:20:33.519
Don't bring him up.

00:20:35.720 --> 00:20:36.799
Gong Lili is back.

00:20:39.599 --> 00:20:40.799
Her kid has grown up.

00:20:41.759 --> 00:20:43.000
Why did they come back?

00:20:44.759 --> 00:20:46.920
Aren't you buying Zhang Hao
an apartment today?

00:20:47.400 --> 00:20:48.000
It's serious.

00:20:48.000 --> 00:20:49.559
Go ahead. I'll be around here.

00:20:50.039 --> 00:20:51.599
I thought about it all night.

00:20:51.599 --> 00:20:53.160
Maybe we should postpone it

00:20:53.160 --> 00:20:54.480
and pay off your debts first.

00:20:55.880 --> 00:20:57.240
Don't worry about me.

00:20:57.839 --> 00:20:59.640
You'd have died
if I hadn't looked after you,

00:20:59.640 --> 00:21:01.279
with your blood pressure hitting 180.

00:21:01.680 --> 00:21:05.240
It never hits 180.
You make it sound like I'm dying.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:11.799
Aunt Hua.

00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:13.799
You brought food?

00:21:14.160 --> 00:21:15.319
What did you make today?

00:21:16.119 --> 00:21:17.319
I made fish.

00:21:17.792 --> 00:21:19.279
The vendor said it just came in.

00:21:19.759 --> 00:21:21.920
Fresh fish is the best.

00:21:21.920 --> 00:21:23.920
I wanted to cook a whole fish for you,

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:27.400
but my pot was too small,
so I cut it into pieces.

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:29.640
What else?

00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:30.759
There's broccoli.

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:33.920
I know you don't like broccoli,

00:21:33.920 --> 00:21:36.480
but they say it's good
for blood pressure.

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:37.759
It's not every day.

00:21:38.039 --> 00:21:39.480
Just have it five times a week.

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:41.400
Seven days a week. Five times?

00:21:41.400 --> 00:21:42.960
That's basically every day.

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:44.720
How's your blood pressure today?

00:21:45.119 --> 00:21:45.839
180.

00:21:47.279 --> 00:21:48.519
Relax. I'm watching him.

00:21:48.799 --> 00:21:50.480
I don't let him drink at night.

00:21:51.279 --> 00:21:53.759
She doesn't sing opera
and I don't beat the drums.

00:21:53.759 --> 00:21:55.160
What should I do besides drink?

00:21:55.799 --> 00:21:56.512
Want some drinks?

00:21:57.000 --> 00:21:57.559
New arrivals.

00:21:58.079 --> 00:22:00.039
They say young people love these.

00:22:01.039 --> 00:22:02.640
(Enrollment)
Once this trainee class starts,

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:04.440
business will boom.

00:22:05.680 --> 00:22:07.880
Once this batch of students graduates,

00:22:07.880 --> 00:22:10.359
you guys could go from having shows
to having none

00:22:10.759 --> 00:22:12.480
just like that.

00:22:13.319 --> 00:22:15.200
Aunt Hua, you guys eat first.

00:22:15.680 --> 00:22:16.519
I have to go.

00:22:24.440 --> 00:22:25.960
Look at you,

00:22:26.680 --> 00:22:27.759
all sulky.

00:22:28.079 --> 00:22:30.720
She brings you meals every day.
Does she owe you?

00:22:31.119 --> 00:22:31.799
Yes, she does.

00:22:33.039 --> 00:22:34.720
She owes me until she sings opera.

00:22:36.400 --> 00:22:37.559
So unreasonable.

00:22:39.559 --> 00:22:40.079
I'm off.

00:22:40.519 --> 00:22:42.240
Where are you going? You didn't eat.

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:43.039
To settle a debt.

00:23:11.079 --> 00:23:12.359
We need to talk business.

00:23:12.359 --> 00:23:13.079
I have no money.

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:14.799
Come on, look at you.

00:23:14.799 --> 00:23:16.119
Why are you like that?

00:23:17.160 --> 00:23:18.839
I went around after I got out.

00:23:19.039 --> 00:23:20.279
My goodness.

00:23:20.279 --> 00:23:21.559
The world has changed.

00:23:22.319 --> 00:23:25.480
Look, everything's so vibrant now.

00:23:25.480 --> 00:23:27.720
Even the men's soccer team
made it to the World Cup.

00:23:28.200 --> 00:23:29.640
What's that got to do with you?

00:23:30.480 --> 00:23:31.680
Everything.

00:23:31.960 --> 00:23:32.799
It shows

00:23:33.480 --> 00:23:35.559
that the country
is developing in all aspects.

00:23:35.880 --> 00:23:38.119
If you repay me now,
I can grow my business.

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:39.319
Yeah.

00:23:40.319 --> 00:23:41.920
Grow your business and go to jail.

00:23:42.880 --> 00:23:45.359
That's not a nice thing to say.

00:23:45.359 --> 00:23:47.279
Things are different from before.

00:23:47.279 --> 00:23:48.440
I'm a remade man.

00:23:48.799 --> 00:23:51.519
This time, I'm going to
do legitimate business.

00:23:53.279 --> 00:23:54.144
You don't believe me?

00:23:54.640 --> 00:23:57.880
A buddy of mine is selling valves cheap.
He runs the factory in Wenzhou.

00:23:58.160 --> 00:24:01.839
If I buy those valves,
I can sell them at twice the price.

00:24:01.839 --> 00:24:03.400
Pay me back now.

00:24:03.400 --> 00:24:05.039
I need the money to turn things around.

00:24:05.559 --> 00:24:06.359
Valves?

00:24:06.359 --> 00:24:07.319
Yeah.

00:24:07.880 --> 00:24:09.640
Every construction site needs valves.

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:11.279
Just look around.

00:24:11.279 --> 00:24:12.960
Chang'an is full of construction sites.

00:24:13.359 --> 00:24:15.559
You can't build houses
without construction sites.

00:24:15.559 --> 00:24:17.640
And those construction sites
will need valves.

00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:18.920
So these valves...

00:24:19.759 --> 00:24:21.839
Forget it. You wouldn't understand.

00:24:21.839 --> 00:24:22.759
You just don't get it.

00:24:24.559 --> 00:24:25.279
Here's the deal.

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:27.240
I'll take the loss.

00:24:28.519 --> 00:24:31.200
Just repay the 30,000 yuan.
I'll waive the interest.

00:24:31.759 --> 00:24:32.640
Over the years,

00:24:33.119 --> 00:24:35.200
I've repaid nearly twice the principal.

00:24:35.559 --> 00:24:39.559
What you paid earlier
was for the 3% interest.

00:24:39.559 --> 00:24:41.119
You never returned the principal.

00:24:41.920 --> 00:24:44.119
Starting today,

00:24:44.119 --> 00:24:45.160
you have one week.

00:24:45.160 --> 00:24:47.559
Just give me back the 30,000 principal,

00:24:47.559 --> 00:24:49.839
and I'll forget the interest, okay?

00:24:55.799 --> 00:24:57.279
Here's the kitchen.

00:24:57.279 --> 00:24:58.599
L-shaped and spacious.

00:24:58.599 --> 00:24:59.400
Here.

00:25:01.079 --> 00:25:04.319
The range hood and gas stove
are included.

00:25:04.319 --> 00:25:06.799
And we've got the natural gas hooked up.

00:25:06.799 --> 00:25:08.000
It's ready for use.

00:25:08.319 --> 00:25:10.359
Just tidy up and move right in.

00:25:10.359 --> 00:25:11.680
- No problem.
- Put the TV there.

00:25:11.839 --> 00:25:12.400
No problem.

00:25:13.039 --> 00:25:13.839
It can go here too.

00:25:13.839 --> 00:25:15.400
- 80,000 is too much.
- It can go here too.

00:25:15.400 --> 00:25:16.880
Is there room for negotiation?

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:19.319
Please, Ma'am, just ask around.

00:25:19.319 --> 00:25:22.319
This is the cheapest apartment
in the area.

00:25:25.279 --> 00:25:27.680
We didn't renovate this place ourselves.

00:25:28.279 --> 00:25:30.559
We're not sure
if the utilities work properly.

00:25:30.559 --> 00:25:33.000
See? The light doesn't work.

00:25:33.359 --> 00:25:36.480
It could be the bulb or faulty wiring.

00:25:36.480 --> 00:25:37.039
Well...

00:25:37.039 --> 00:25:40.279
The place is empty.
We'll need to buy furniture.

00:25:40.279 --> 00:25:42.759
And the baby is coming soon.
That costs money.

00:25:44.319 --> 00:25:45.359
Shall we keep looking?

00:25:45.720 --> 00:25:47.880
Mom, Ning's due any day.

00:25:47.880 --> 00:25:49.599
She won't be able to move later.

00:25:50.119 --> 00:25:51.440
We've seen so many places.

00:25:51.880 --> 00:25:54.160
This one seems quite suitable.

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:55.920
Yeah, Ma'am.

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:59.200
Apartment prices will only keep rising.

00:25:59.200 --> 00:26:01.559
You know Chunxiao Garden
around the Giant Wild Goose Pagoda?

00:26:01.559 --> 00:26:02.920
That was all farmland before.

00:26:02.920 --> 00:26:05.240
They built a sales office
and started selling apartments.

00:26:05.240 --> 00:26:07.799
It's reaching 10,000 yuan
per square meter.

00:26:08.240 --> 00:26:08.759
Mom.

00:26:08.759 --> 00:26:11.039
I really think it's quite a good deal.

00:26:11.039 --> 00:26:11.880
Yeah.

00:26:12.400 --> 00:26:14.599
Mom, I'm really happy with this place.

00:26:18.799 --> 00:26:21.480
So this is it?

00:26:21.480 --> 00:26:22.279
- Yeah.
- Alright.

00:26:22.279 --> 00:26:23.839
Then let's sign the contract.

00:26:23.839 --> 00:26:24.559
Over here, Ma'am.

00:26:24.559 --> 00:26:25.640
- I think it's nice.
- Here.

00:26:25.640 --> 00:26:26.960
Right?

00:26:26.960 --> 00:26:28.799
Please sit, Ma'am.
Let me get the contract.

00:26:29.519 --> 00:26:30.640
I brought it with me.

00:26:33.599 --> 00:26:35.160
Here, Ma'am, take a look.

00:26:37.160 --> 00:26:39.039
- This is the contract.
- Zhang Hao.

00:26:39.039 --> 00:26:40.079
Zhang Hao, come here.

00:26:41.480 --> 00:26:43.000
This room is big enough.

00:26:43.000 --> 00:26:44.920
My mom and my brother can stay here.

00:26:48.240 --> 00:26:49.680
If there are no problems,

00:26:49.680 --> 00:26:52.720
sign and put your fingerprint
on the last page.

00:26:53.799 --> 00:26:54.519
Here, Ma'am.

00:26:57.240 --> 00:26:58.000
Zhang Hao.

00:26:58.519 --> 00:26:59.200
Mom.

00:26:59.200 --> 00:27:00.119
Come sign.

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:04.288
Here.

00:27:04.799 --> 00:27:06.039
Just sign here.

00:27:08.680 --> 00:27:10.480
And put your fingerprint on your name.

00:27:11.921 --> 00:27:23.200
笙ｪMother, please don't
shed any more tears笙ｪ

00:27:23.200 --> 00:27:24.880
How's the person I introduced to you?

00:27:25.640 --> 00:27:26.480
She sings well.

00:27:27.000 --> 00:27:29.759
But she's old. That's not an advantage.

00:27:31.880 --> 00:27:33.319
She's singing without makeup.

00:27:33.680 --> 00:27:35.799
Do her makeup and dress her up.

00:27:35.799 --> 00:27:37.039
She'll look younger.

00:27:37.039 --> 00:27:37.839
Let's listen to

00:27:38.359 --> 00:27:39.920
what the audience says.

00:27:40.559 --> 00:27:42.000
Alright, go ahead.

00:27:42.000 --> 00:27:43.000
We're confident.

00:27:54.759 --> 00:27:56.519
Two Draping Red from Mr. Shi.

00:27:57.400 --> 00:27:58.880
Five Draping Red from Mr. Xie.

00:27:59.319 --> 00:28:00.559
See? She got tips.

00:28:01.799 --> 00:28:02.440
Just this?

00:28:03.119 --> 00:28:04.880
Prostate level.

00:28:05.440 --> 00:28:06.279
What do you mean?

00:28:07.599 --> 00:28:09.680
It's just dribbling.

00:28:10.240 --> 00:28:11.759
That's a nasty thing to say.

00:28:12.839 --> 00:28:14.039
It's better than nothing.

00:28:14.039 --> 00:28:16.400
You've seen performers
without any Draping Red.

00:28:17.039 --> 00:28:19.640
Your audience comes for the opera.

00:28:19.640 --> 00:28:21.640
They know the deal, alright?

00:28:21.640 --> 00:28:23.240
But their appreciation

00:28:23.240 --> 00:28:24.759
doesn't put food on the table.

00:28:25.119 --> 00:28:26.960
The price has gone up for everything.

00:28:26.960 --> 00:28:28.400
The rent has doubled.

00:28:28.960 --> 00:28:30.200
And the salary is rising.

00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:32.759
It's 100 yuan for every extra worker.

00:28:33.079 --> 00:28:34.160
Only my tea

00:28:34.519 --> 00:28:37.000
is still ten yuan a pot.
That hasn't changed.

00:28:37.480 --> 00:28:38.400
It has changed.

00:28:38.400 --> 00:28:40.039
You changed the tea to tea dust.

00:28:41.799 --> 00:28:42.920
With an extra worker,

00:28:42.920 --> 00:28:44.279
you pay an extra 100 yuan.

00:28:44.799 --> 00:28:47.039
But the show is almost an hour longer.

00:28:47.640 --> 00:28:49.279
You're haggling over this?

00:28:50.359 --> 00:28:51.079
Look.

00:28:51.599 --> 00:28:54.440
Get your niece, Yi Qin'e.

00:28:54.799 --> 00:28:55.720
I'll raise it.

00:28:56.079 --> 00:28:58.319
I'll triple it.

00:29:01.279 --> 00:29:01.960
What?

00:29:02.480 --> 00:29:04.160
She hasn't performed in years?

00:29:06.039 --> 00:29:07.359
Did she really quit?

00:29:10.519 --> 00:29:14.680
There will never be another Yi Qin'e.

00:29:15.359 --> 00:29:16.200
Forget it.

00:29:16.799 --> 00:29:19.039
What do you say? Let's settle this.

00:29:19.640 --> 00:29:20.359
Alright.

00:29:21.000 --> 00:29:23.960
For the sake of Ms. Yi,
let her come and sing.

00:29:24.082 --> 00:29:26.320
(Qinqiang Opera:
Dragon and Phoenix Bringing Prosperity)

00:29:26.480 --> 00:29:27.136
Alright.

00:30:53.559 --> 00:30:58.160
笙ｪGaze at笙ｪ

00:30:58.839 --> 00:31:03.440
笙ｪMy mother笙ｪ

00:31:03.759 --> 00:31:04.640
Stop.

00:31:05.160 --> 00:31:06.640
Sing out.

00:31:07.200 --> 00:31:10.920
笙ｪGaze at笙ｪ

00:31:10.920 --> 00:31:12.359
Take a breath. Sing.

00:31:12.640 --> 00:31:14.920
笙ｪMy mother笙ｪ

00:31:14.920 --> 00:31:15.920
There you go.

00:31:17.480 --> 00:31:18.480
Very good.

00:31:23.319 --> 00:31:28.400
笙ｪNo need to mention the trifles笙ｪ

00:31:33.960 --> 00:31:35.008
Who are you looking for?

00:31:36.039 --> 00:31:37.240
Your Troupe Leader.

00:31:37.240 --> 00:31:38.440
That's me.

00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:41.240
Who are you?

00:31:49.720 --> 00:31:50.240
Mr. Liu.

00:31:51.000 --> 00:31:51.920
What can I do for you?

00:31:53.200 --> 00:31:54.016
I want some opera.

00:31:55.079 --> 00:31:57.119
Come to the theater in the evening.

00:31:59.079 --> 00:32:00.400
I'm booking a play.

00:32:01.359 --> 00:32:02.319
You're booking a play?

00:32:03.920 --> 00:32:05.519
Let's go to the Business Department.

00:32:06.200 --> 00:32:07.680
Which opera do you want to book?

00:32:08.319 --> 00:32:09.240
Yi Qin'e.

00:32:10.039 --> 00:32:11.279
She's not available.

00:32:12.119 --> 00:32:13.480
Can I get you someone else?

00:32:15.440 --> 00:32:17.200
Set your terms.

00:32:17.200 --> 00:32:18.640
Name your price.

00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:22.000
But one thing. We only want Yi Qin'e.

00:32:22.599 --> 00:32:23.960
She doesn't sing anymore.

00:32:24.440 --> 00:32:25.319
She stopped singing?

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:26.960
You didn't know?

00:32:26.960 --> 00:32:28.039
Why did she stop?

00:32:29.880 --> 00:32:32.680
After that stage collapse,
she couldn't sing anymore.

00:32:33.240 --> 00:32:35.559
Her health failed in the first year.

00:32:36.000 --> 00:32:38.000
In the second year, she had a breakdown.

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:40.039
In the third year, she quit outright.

00:32:40.599 --> 00:32:41.880
Even her uncle has given up.

00:32:42.480 --> 00:32:43.440
For real?

00:32:43.440 --> 00:32:44.319
Of course.

00:32:44.880 --> 00:32:46.279
Well...

00:32:46.279 --> 00:32:47.759
Where's her Uncle Sanyuan?

00:32:48.319 --> 00:32:49.400
Can it be cheaper?

00:32:49.920 --> 00:32:51.759
Three for six yuan.

00:32:52.000 --> 00:32:53.279
Why do I need so many basins?

00:32:53.279 --> 00:32:54.759
One for two-fifty.

00:32:57.039 --> 00:32:58.240
You can't park here.

00:32:59.119 --> 00:33:00.160
It's blocking the road.

00:33:02.880 --> 00:33:03.599
Uncle Sanyuan.

00:33:05.519 --> 00:33:06.279
Who are you?

00:33:07.200 --> 00:33:09.200
Master Gu's apprentice, Liu Situan.

00:33:10.000 --> 00:33:10.560
Situan.

00:33:11.240 --> 00:33:11.839
Uncle.

00:33:11.839 --> 00:33:13.248
You gained weight. I couldn't tell.

00:33:13.519 --> 00:33:14.039
That's right.

00:33:14.359 --> 00:33:17.440
Now that I've gained weight,
I fit the car even better.

00:33:20.119 --> 00:33:20.920
She quit

00:33:21.519 --> 00:33:22.599
a long time ago.

00:33:23.559 --> 00:33:25.079
She quit? Why?

00:33:25.480 --> 00:33:26.240
Her voice gave out?

00:33:26.720 --> 00:33:28.000
She just won't sing anymore.

00:33:30.640 --> 00:33:33.480
Uncle, why are you
selling newspapers here?

00:33:34.319 --> 00:33:36.880
I sell books, magazines, newspapers,

00:33:37.480 --> 00:33:38.559
and drinks.

00:33:38.559 --> 00:33:40.039
I also run two pool tables.

00:33:40.279 --> 00:33:41.319
Whatever comes along.

00:33:42.000 --> 00:33:44.000
I sell daily necessities too.

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:46.079
You just got back.

00:33:46.720 --> 00:33:48.519
You can use some daily items.

00:33:48.519 --> 00:33:49.279
Take some.

00:33:49.519 --> 00:33:50.920
Okay, I'll take some later.

00:33:51.920 --> 00:33:53.759
- Take as much as you want.
- Okay.

00:33:56.599 --> 00:33:58.000
Is your master doing well?

00:33:59.279 --> 00:34:02.000
I don't know. I'm not with him anymore.

00:34:02.880 --> 00:34:05.200
That's why you made it big, huh?

00:34:07.160 --> 00:34:09.319
Your master beat you hard
when you were a kid.

00:34:09.640 --> 00:34:12.160
Every time,
you'd come to me for protection.

00:34:12.160 --> 00:34:13.240
If I hadn't kept you,

00:34:13.599 --> 00:34:16.279
you could've been beaten to death.

00:34:20.039 --> 00:34:21.799
Uncle, are you doing okay?

00:34:21.920 --> 00:34:22.599
I'm just fine.

00:34:23.359 --> 00:34:24.920
How about Qin'e?

00:34:25.519 --> 00:34:27.279
Let's have dinner together.

00:34:27.279 --> 00:34:28.519
It's been so long.

00:34:28.680 --> 00:34:29.536
Let's grab a drink.

00:34:29.759 --> 00:34:30.519
We can't.

00:34:30.880 --> 00:34:31.960
Qin'e has a play tonight.

00:34:32.400 --> 00:34:33.279
I have to wait here.

00:34:33.720 --> 00:34:35.440
Didn't she quit singing? What play?

00:34:36.200 --> 00:34:38.039
She does other theater work.

00:34:40.480 --> 00:34:41.720
You still need to eat.

00:34:41.720 --> 00:34:42.680
What would you like?

00:34:42.680 --> 00:34:44.079
I'll get something for both of us.

00:34:44.079 --> 00:34:46.319
I usually grab a quick bite.

00:34:47.240 --> 00:34:48.279
Anything on your mind?

00:34:54.079 --> 00:34:56.000
I told you to get a quick bite.

00:34:57.480 --> 00:34:58.480
You made it so difficult.

00:34:59.039 --> 00:35:01.200
I'd rather gnaw on a roast chicken.

00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:02.839
And it's expensive.

00:35:03.480 --> 00:35:04.032
Uncle.

00:35:04.400 --> 00:35:05.319
Dig in.

00:35:07.319 --> 00:35:08.000
Look.

00:35:08.519 --> 00:35:10.720
You got all your daily supplies at once.

00:35:12.160 --> 00:35:13.240
Your car is loaded.

00:35:14.200 --> 00:35:15.359
Those could cost you

00:35:15.359 --> 00:35:17.759
- 1000 yuan in the supermarket.
- Yeah.

00:35:17.759 --> 00:35:20.279
I filled your car for only 560.

00:35:20.720 --> 00:35:22.440
I'll round it down to 550, okay?

00:35:23.240 --> 00:35:25.640
Alright, Uncle. Whatever you say.

00:35:27.720 --> 00:35:29.599
Here, 600 yuan.

00:35:29.599 --> 00:35:31.039
Keep the change.

00:35:31.039 --> 00:35:31.880
This won't do.

00:35:31.880 --> 00:35:33.319
- Take it.
- Come on...

00:35:33.599 --> 00:35:34.400
Come on.

00:35:35.480 --> 00:35:37.200
Come back tomorrow.

00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:39.279
Get some thermoses

00:35:39.839 --> 00:35:41.279
and pillowcases.

00:35:42.799 --> 00:35:43.488
Okay.

00:35:43.920 --> 00:35:44.544
Uncle.

00:35:44.920 --> 00:35:47.360
I forgot to ask you.
What is Qin'e working on?

00:35:49.119 --> 00:35:49.920
The coat trunk.

00:35:50.719 --> 00:35:51.280
What?

00:35:52.239 --> 00:35:54.199
She quit singing, but she could direct.

00:35:54.800 --> 00:35:56.320
Why is she serving the others?

00:35:57.800 --> 00:35:58.760
Who assigned her that?

00:35:59.000 --> 00:36:00.599
The Troupe Leader, Xue Guisheng.

00:36:02.400 --> 00:36:03.280
I'm telling you.

00:36:04.960 --> 00:36:07.639
Troupe Leader Shan passed away,
and everything fell apart.

00:36:08.360 --> 00:36:09.760
Worthless trash.

00:36:09.760 --> 00:36:10.800
They messed it up.

00:36:11.360 --> 00:36:12.599
No plays to rehearse.

00:36:12.599 --> 00:36:13.679
No plays to perform.

00:36:14.239 --> 00:36:15.760
And Qin'e is managing costumes.

00:36:15.760 --> 00:36:17.519
Such a star performer is left unused.

00:36:17.519 --> 00:36:18.079
You know,

00:36:19.159 --> 00:36:20.480
she doesn't want to perform.

00:36:20.840 --> 00:36:22.559
They should talk to her.

00:36:23.079 --> 00:36:25.880
They can't just dump her
to handle the coat trunk.

00:36:26.559 --> 00:36:27.280
What a waste.

00:36:27.719 --> 00:36:28.320
Then

00:36:29.239 --> 00:36:31.760
why don't you report him?

00:36:31.760 --> 00:36:33.079
What's there to report?

00:36:37.280 --> 00:36:38.280
Hongbing passed away.

00:36:38.679 --> 00:36:39.719
Xue Guisheng

00:36:40.320 --> 00:36:41.840
wanted to pursue Qin'e.

00:36:43.000 --> 00:36:44.559
Xue Guisheng wanted to pursue Qin'e?

00:36:45.039 --> 00:36:46.719
Keep it down. Stop yelling.

00:36:47.599 --> 00:36:49.039
How could I fancy that guy?

00:36:49.320 --> 00:36:50.519
So I stopped him, of course.

00:36:51.280 --> 00:36:52.544
Qin'e didn't want him either.

00:36:53.400 --> 00:36:54.144
He held a grudge.

00:36:54.239 --> 00:36:57.400
So he used his petty authority
to make things hard for Qin'e.

00:36:58.760 --> 00:36:59.519
You know me.

00:37:00.159 --> 00:37:01.119
I've been to prison.

00:37:01.760 --> 00:37:02.559
I've seen it all.

00:37:02.960 --> 00:37:04.599
I know all his little tricks.

00:37:04.599 --> 00:37:05.719
I'd take him down.

00:37:06.199 --> 00:37:07.840
But Qin'e wouldn't let me.

00:37:08.840 --> 00:37:09.559
Forget it.

00:37:09.559 --> 00:37:10.960
I swallowed my anger

00:37:11.320 --> 00:37:12.599
and set up this stall

00:37:13.559 --> 00:37:15.239
right at the troupe's entrance.

00:37:15.239 --> 00:37:17.079
Let's see who dares to bully Qin'e.

00:37:21.519 --> 00:37:22.679
Come on, drink up.

00:37:35.480 --> 00:37:36.559
Had some drinks again?

00:37:38.599 --> 00:37:39.199
Nice, huh?

00:37:39.559 --> 00:37:40.760
Lobster with barbecue.

00:37:41.280 --> 00:37:43.519
Who did you eat with? Fancy meal.

00:37:44.199 --> 00:37:44.880
Situan.

00:37:45.960 --> 00:37:46.719
Situan?

00:37:47.239 --> 00:37:48.280
Remember Liu Situan?

00:37:49.360 --> 00:37:50.440
Master Gu's apprentice.

00:37:50.639 --> 00:37:51.519
The coat trunk guy.

00:37:52.559 --> 00:37:54.559
He made it big and came in a Mercedes.

00:37:55.000 --> 00:37:55.679
Really?

00:37:55.679 --> 00:37:56.440
Absolutely.

00:37:57.079 --> 00:37:57.880
Here.

00:38:00.239 --> 00:38:02.079
Look, I saved you some.

00:38:04.559 --> 00:38:05.239
My goodness.

00:38:06.239 --> 00:38:08.079
You look like you've had a few.

00:38:08.672 --> 00:38:10.320
Did you spout nonsense again?

00:38:13.440 --> 00:38:13.960
Listen.

00:38:15.159 --> 00:38:16.239
Liu Situan

00:38:17.840 --> 00:38:20.960
is paying 300,000 to book Qin'e's play.

00:38:21.559 --> 00:38:23.440
Who else in Qinqiang opera
gets that offer?

00:38:24.679 --> 00:38:26.000
Why are you so excited?

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:27.800
It has happened before.

00:38:27.800 --> 00:38:29.599
But Laidi can't sing anymore.

00:38:31.840 --> 00:38:34.320
What happened to the girl

00:38:34.320 --> 00:38:37.559
who begged to follow me
to the county and learn opera?

00:38:39.519 --> 00:38:40.360
Now she won't sing?

00:38:41.079 --> 00:38:42.079
Don't stare at me.

00:38:42.599 --> 00:38:44.239
Others may not know, but you do.

00:38:45.800 --> 00:38:48.159
I could've taken her sister instead.

00:38:48.920 --> 00:38:51.480
She chased me crying,
and swapped places with her sister.

00:38:52.119 --> 00:38:55.559
I only brought her out
because I pitied her.

00:38:56.119 --> 00:38:58.840
Why do you keep spouting nonsense?

00:38:58.840 --> 00:39:00.320
How am I spouting nonsense?

00:39:01.280 --> 00:39:03.800
She was working in the kitchen.

00:39:04.320 --> 00:39:06.400
If I hadn't pushed her
to practice every day,

00:39:06.400 --> 00:39:07.519
would she be where she is?

00:39:07.616 --> 00:39:08.840
When she was in the kitchen,

00:39:08.840 --> 00:39:09.639
where were you?

00:39:09.639 --> 00:39:10.239
Where was I?

00:39:10.719 --> 00:39:12.239
You were in prison.

00:39:13.280 --> 00:39:16.639
I gave her a push after I got out,
leading to her success.

00:39:16.880 --> 00:39:17.960
Yeah.

00:39:18.280 --> 00:39:20.719
You made her
the Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera.

00:39:20.719 --> 00:39:21.280
Right?

00:39:21.840 --> 00:39:22.400
Yeah.

00:39:23.239 --> 00:39:24.440
I'm going to travel.

00:39:26.840 --> 00:39:27.559
Where to?

00:39:28.320 --> 00:39:29.800
I'm invited to a seminar

00:39:30.800 --> 00:39:31.840
in Shenzhen.

00:39:31.960 --> 00:39:34.079
Seminar on Qinqiang opera in Shenzhen?

00:39:34.599 --> 00:39:36.079
Seminar on a catering franchise.

00:39:36.559 --> 00:39:38.119
Franchising's the future.

00:39:38.719 --> 00:39:42.079
Tofu Beauty is one of
the earliest catering franchises.

00:39:42.480 --> 00:39:44.039
I'm going to share my expertise.

00:39:46.159 --> 00:39:47.400
You're ruining the craft.

00:39:47.719 --> 00:39:49.039
Catering franchises?

00:39:49.840 --> 00:39:51.039
Think about your generation

00:39:51.280 --> 00:39:53.000
and the "Cun" generation.

00:39:53.880 --> 00:39:55.880
They died on stage.

00:39:56.400 --> 00:39:58.440
Such dedication to Qinqiang opera.

00:40:00.119 --> 00:40:02.559
Who promised to uphold Qinqiang opera?

00:40:05.280 --> 00:40:07.000
We go through stages in life.

00:40:07.360 --> 00:40:09.559
First, mountains are just mountains.

00:40:10.039 --> 00:40:12.320
Then, mountains are no longer mountains.

00:40:13.679 --> 00:40:16.000
Finally, mountains are still mountains.

00:40:16.000 --> 00:40:17.480
Let go of your obsession.

00:40:18.400 --> 00:40:19.639
Don't give me that.

00:40:21.159 --> 00:40:22.559
I have obsessions?

00:40:22.920 --> 00:40:24.639
Who keeps going around backstage,

00:40:25.239 --> 00:40:27.440
showing people
his lousy, unfinished script,

00:40:27.800 --> 00:40:29.400
trying to sell it?

00:40:29.440 --> 00:40:31.719
We see it differently.

00:40:32.639 --> 00:40:33.760
In my opinion...

00:40:33.880 --> 00:40:34.760
Different how?

00:40:35.559 --> 00:40:36.840
Your words count.

00:40:37.719 --> 00:40:39.559
Who said that the land's yield

00:40:39.559 --> 00:40:41.800
is limited only by human audacity

00:40:43.320 --> 00:40:46.039
and told me to stuff that cannon barrel
with gunpowder?

00:40:46.519 --> 00:40:47.199
It killed someone

00:40:47.559 --> 00:40:48.840
and ruined my face.

00:40:51.559 --> 00:40:52.239
Stop staring.

00:40:53.719 --> 00:40:54.320
Keep playing.

00:41:03.119 --> 00:41:03.760
What happened?

00:41:04.119 --> 00:41:05.239
Why did a police car

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:07.360
come to the troupe?

00:41:09.559 --> 00:41:11.679
This is a society ruled by law.
Abide by the law.

00:41:11.679 --> 00:41:13.000
Don't fight.

00:41:13.360 --> 00:41:14.840
Fighting in front of the police?

00:41:14.840 --> 00:41:15.519
Are you crazy?

00:41:16.320 --> 00:41:17.840
Tell us. What happened?

00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:19.239
How would I know?

00:41:19.639 --> 00:41:21.039
I was just working.

00:41:21.679 --> 00:41:24.440
This guy beat me up
without saying a word.

00:41:24.440 --> 00:41:26.119
Look at what he did to me.

00:41:26.119 --> 00:41:26.800
That's right.

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:27.800
He's not our staff

00:41:27.800 --> 00:41:29.119
and just showed up.

00:41:29.119 --> 00:41:30.360
You deserve it.

00:41:32.360 --> 00:41:33.639
Why did you hit him?

00:41:33.639 --> 00:41:34.519
He abused his power.

00:41:34.880 --> 00:41:35.639
What?

00:41:36.960 --> 00:41:37.480
Everyone.

00:41:37.800 --> 00:41:39.960
Do you know
why Yi Qin'e stopped performing?

00:41:39.960 --> 00:41:41.000
- Why?
- Why?

00:41:41.440 --> 00:41:42.400
Because he failed

00:41:42.519 --> 00:41:43.480
to win her over.

00:41:43.719 --> 00:41:45.679
Then he made her manage the costumes.

00:41:46.079 --> 00:41:48.000
The Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera

00:41:48.039 --> 00:41:48.920
can't be mistreated.

00:41:49.000 --> 00:41:50.320
Aren't you humiliating her?

00:41:50.320 --> 00:41:51.000
For real?

00:41:51.000 --> 00:41:53.599
You performed with Yi Qin'e
for so many years.

00:41:53.599 --> 00:41:55.719
You think you can do whatever you want

00:41:56.239 --> 00:41:57.639
now that you're the Troupe Leader?

00:41:57.639 --> 00:41:59.960
You think all the actresses
belong to you?

00:41:59.960 --> 00:42:01.320
Hey, watch your tongue.

00:42:01.320 --> 00:42:02.400
Nonsense!

00:42:03.519 --> 00:42:05.039
I'll rip your mouth off.

00:42:05.639 --> 00:42:06.880
Everyone, calm down.

00:42:06.880 --> 00:42:07.400
Assault!

00:42:07.400 --> 00:42:08.239
What are you doing?

00:42:08.239 --> 00:42:09.039
Uncle Sanyuan.

00:42:09.039 --> 00:42:09.840
Stay out of it.

00:42:10.119 --> 00:42:11.199
I was gone.

00:42:11.679 --> 00:42:12.760
But now I'm back.

00:42:12.760 --> 00:42:14.559
I will stand up for you and Qin'e.

00:42:14.559 --> 00:42:15.800
Stop compromising.

00:42:15.800 --> 00:42:16.639
What nonsense!

00:42:16.639 --> 00:42:17.679
Are you crazy?

00:42:18.320 --> 00:42:19.159
Officer.

00:42:19.159 --> 00:42:19.800
I'm sorry.

00:42:20.199 --> 00:42:21.920
It's a misunderstanding.

00:42:21.920 --> 00:42:23.264
We hope it's a misunderstanding.

00:42:23.719 --> 00:42:26.800
But since we've been dispatched,
we need a resolution and a report.

00:42:26.800 --> 00:42:27.480
Can you

00:42:28.239 --> 00:42:29.079
settle this?

00:42:29.199 --> 00:42:30.079
No problem.

00:42:30.639 --> 00:42:31.519
We'll settle this.

00:42:32.639 --> 00:42:33.248
Troupe Leader.

00:42:34.079 --> 00:42:35.599
We don't want this to blow up.

00:42:35.599 --> 00:42:36.639
Solve it privately.

00:42:37.199 --> 00:42:37.920
Come on.

00:42:38.519 --> 00:42:40.079
- He humiliated me.
- Yeah.

00:42:40.079 --> 00:42:41.599
I'll make him apologize.

00:42:42.000 --> 00:42:43.239
- Apologize. Now.
- No.

00:42:44.039 --> 00:42:45.400
Apologize to him.

00:42:45.800 --> 00:42:46.519
Apologize.

00:42:46.960 --> 00:42:47.760
What are you doing?

00:42:47.760 --> 00:42:48.280
Apologize.

00:42:51.119 --> 00:42:51.800
I apologize.

00:42:52.360 --> 00:42:53.440
Or 300,000 yuan for a play.

00:42:53.880 --> 00:42:54.559
Your choice.

00:42:55.840 --> 00:42:57.269
Three hundred thousand?

00:43:00.559 --> 00:43:02.920
Three hundred thousand for a play.

00:43:05.120 --> 00:43:06.921
(Preview)

00:43:08.741 --> 00:43:11.260
I knew I couldn't keep this from you.

00:43:11.260 --> 00:43:13.541
Who's causing trouble? Do I know them?

00:43:13.860 --> 00:43:15.021
You definitely know them.

00:43:15.021 --> 00:43:16.581
I could do better than Liu Hongbing.

00:43:16.820 --> 00:43:19.300
If you dare pester Qin'e,
I'll fight you to the death.

00:43:19.501 --> 00:43:20.661
How am I worse than him?

00:43:21.181 --> 00:43:24.420
Fate isn't in your face,
hands, or birth charts,

00:43:24.420 --> 00:43:25.940
but in your own heart.

00:43:25.940 --> 00:43:28.221
I came for the trainee class.
I want to sing opera.

00:43:28.221 --> 00:43:30.181
She's Master Song's kid.
You should look after her.

00:43:30.940 --> 00:43:32.181
Change and come with me.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
笙ｪWhen I woke up and turned back笙ｪ

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
笙ｪI wasn't sure where to go笙ｪ

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
笙ｪWe met and brushed past笙ｪ

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
笙ｪYour shadow drifted out of sight笙ｪ

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
笙ｪThe stove fire blazed in my dream笙ｪ

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
笙ｪLit up the tracks of pearly tears笙ｪ

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
笙ｪIn my dream, water sleeves flew笙ｪ

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
笙ｪHiding a lifetime of love笙ｪ

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
笙ｪThe Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage笙ｪ

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
笙ｪSpring water brewed strong wine笙ｪ

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
笙ｪSheep moved through the valley笙ｪ

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
笙ｪIt felt like a promise
from another life笙ｪ

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
笙ｪWhen I woke up and turned back笙ｪ

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
笙ｪI wasn't sure where to go笙ｪ

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
笙ｪIf I chose again, I'd still roam笙ｪ

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
笙ｪAll over this sunlit plateau笙ｪ

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
笙ｪThe dream ends; the curtain falls笙ｪ

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
笙ｪMoonlight washes off this stage makeup笙ｪ

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
笙ｪThe one in the mirror wears gray hair笙ｪ

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
笙ｪAlready sang all my joy and sorrow笙ｪ

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
笙ｪAlready shouted across Qinchuan Plain笙ｪ